{"tid":91231,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女友對我忽冷忽熱","createTime":"2017-01-22T16:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T13:51:33.000Z","uid":71465,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"101241f7d0ab00b1ce31f5d88a045d1a044226c8","tid":91231,"uid":71465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:34:05.000Z","msg":"同佢啱啱開始 自問都幾鐘意佢<br />\n不過佢成日對我忽冷忽熱<br />\n有時會話掛著我個d嘢<br />\n但有時又話唔想見住<br />\n所以有時會唔知佢想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似話雙子座嘅人係忽冷忽熱 而佢正正係雙子座<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢曾經好鐘意一個人 但人地只當佢朋友<br />\n不過佢講過嗰個人肯追佢嘅話 佢一定會接受 <br />\n然後就飛咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然話佢地已經冇咩聯絡 <br />\n但我都有d擔心我地嘅關係會俾嗰個人一手破壞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">其實我都知自己只係個水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"16a55e56e2064a6c5ab5e16436fdfda9200af33d","tid":91231,"uid":71465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d6716f7ed6a7efd22e9d58c60d76d531a3faab","tid":91231,"uid":71465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:35:06.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以解釋下？"},{"pid":"b74136c7448afaa025c3482f317924ff532ea546","tid":91231,"uid":71465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be55fca862e7c8a0e349b3298b35a241a47f39c6","tid":91231,"uid":47250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢真係似係當你水泡，你唯有表明再主動d 再暖男d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"